# API

> Primary data path today is client-side wagmi/viem. Use API routes only when server-side is required.

## Always

- Route handlers: `app/api/<resource>/route.ts`
- HTTP clients live in `services/`; components use React Query with `staleTime`, retry ≤ 3
- Handle loading, error, empty, timeout in UI
- JSON shape: `{ code: "success" | string, msg: string, data: T }` — `code === "success"` 表示成功，否则失败（`msg` 用于错误提示）
- Server secrets without `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix

## Never

- Raw `fetch()` inside React components
- Leak stack traces, RPC URLs, or secrets in responses
- Server-side signing without explicit security review
